text: Makenna Gabrielle Cowgill (born 11 September 1998) is an American actress. She has provided voices for many animated movies. == Filmography == *Bambi II (2006) *Meet the Robinsons (2007) *The Time Traveler's Wife (2009) *Diary of a Wimpy Kid (2010) *Monsters University (2013) == References == == Other websites == * Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Connecticut Category:Living people Category:1998 births
